== Storm names ==
The following names were used for named storms that formed in the north Atlantic in 2003. The names not retired from this list will be used again in the [[2009 Atlantic hurricane season|2009 season]]. This is the same list used for the [[1997 Atlantic hurricane season|1997 season]]. Storms were named Larry, Mindy, Nicholas, Odette, and Peter for the first time in 2003. Names that were not assigned are marked in {{tcname unused}}.

