* {{tcname unused|Victor}}
* {{tcname unused|Wanda}}
|}

=== Retirement ===
{{seealso|List of retired Atlantic hurricane names}}
The [[World Meteorological Organization]] retired three names in the spring of 2004: Fabian, Isabel, and Juan. They will be replaced in the [[2009 Atlantic hurricane season|2009 season]] by Fred, Ida, and Joaquin respectively.<ref name="2003wmo"/>

